
very first time need to bootstrap model
bash> touch model

to reset
bash> rm model_n1 calc_min_trending trending; >model

run as (or whatever the pig format is, 
bash> pig -x local -param next_block_file=2grams_over_day.test.part00 trending.pig

examine result
bash> sort model_n1
bash> sort calc_min_trending
bash> sort trending

next time through
bash> mv model_n1 model; rm calc_min_trending trending
bash> pig -x local -param next_block_file=2grams_over_day.test.part01 trending.pig

